This lovely two cant wait to play with their new toy from @milknplay.sg! Bought them this BeginAgain balance boat that combines colour and shape learning, shape sorting, and balance game play all in one! How fun?! Swipe > to see 👀

It made from eco-friendly rubberwood and is finished with water based stains. Promote fine motor skills and puzzles that help improve cognitive functions, definitely is a perfect gift for every child no matter the age or the occasion!

Quote 'makfamily15' for 15% off with no min spend required! Valid till 31 Oct 2020 😊 dont miss it okay!
